## Phase 
    Beta

## Audience
- 11 potential customers

## We were focusing on 
‐ Fair Work Awareness
‐ Fair Work attitudes and commitment ‐ Fair Work Themes
‐ Fair Work examples
‐ Fair Work Evidence
‐ Fair Work Tool 


| Learning
| ---
|	There is very low general awareness of Fair Work or any of the related terms
|	Most people have heard of the Living Wage, but don’t actually know how much it is
| Living wage is the stated "Sticking point" with many smaller comapnies
| Gender Gap is teh "Invisible" issue that people are blind to.


